{"tid":489519,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大 嘥 鬼","createTime":"2017-12-04T17:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T19:47:19.000Z","uid":117525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b8897a0775b2ed7d8b9f3b8e8166a20e346391e6","tid":489519,"uid":117525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"無錯 我就係要講大嘥鬼 因為個人認為大嘥鬼算係超越垃圾蟲嘅代言人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2013年環境局搞咗呢隻嘢出嚟 <br />\n大嘥鬼個形象好鮮明 雖然個樣就真係唔係咁討好 但一講眼闊肚窄大家已經明白隻騎呢嘢係宣傳啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上廣告一播夜播 用一首Rap好快就令全香港人知毫大嘥鬼係乜<br />\n「眼闊 肚窄 大嘥鬼！食唔曬唔好亂咁嗌啦⋯⋯」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即使係最近蔣志光扮啊Lam唱「冇謂嘥冇謂嘥⋯⋯」一睇歌詞都已經有曬聲畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且班PR跟得好貼 就好似呢兩日謝霆鋒嘅摩打手都會抽下水 仲要抽得好貼題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/005517_c6cba2842cdec74942e249648201ee23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F005517_c6cba2842cdec74942e249648201ee23.jpg&h=cfed785f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/010938_3f1d62095446b332ed5f7c221ed72cd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F010938_3f1d62095446b332ed5f7c221ed72cd2.jpg&h=16392eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前都有巴打就住呢個大嘥鬼post讚班PR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一方面 大嘥鬼個老竇黃錦星成日都好落力sell佢個仔 出席大小event都會著住大嘥鬼Tshirt 又會周不時喺褲袋拎幾隻用百家布縫成嘅大嘥鬼出嚟同啲記者hard sell下 係抵呢隻嘢紅嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗱講明啊 唔係政府打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而係覺得睇到近年政府做每樣嘢都好嘔心個陣 突然發現咗大嘥鬼嘅好 而且環保喺香港真係好需要再發展多啲 <br />\n唔係要做終極環保撚 但最簡單嘅垃圾分類都做唔好 仲話自己係乜柒國際都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至少可以參考下澳洲Dumb ways to die呢種嘅宣傳手法 出下啲周邊商品、Apps等等 將要宣揚嘅訊息再發大嚟搞 <del>更何況港豬係全世界最易被洗腦嘅生物玩潛移默化就啱㗎喇</del> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大嘥鬼班PR我知你哋會睇到呢個post㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好俾大嘥鬼瓜老襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c401b8146d706f607db89a113126f69e2980b12b","tid":489519,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T19:47:19.000Z","msg":"有冇英文名架"}]}